The paper deals with recognizing material properties from images, which is a task that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses using machine learning techniques to recognize these properties, which could fall under machine learning (cs.MM) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses using human perception to gather annotations, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR).
